quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  39,22,"E ko on mo Allah yaﾃｱﾃｱani ﾉ兎rnde mun fii lislaamu, o feewi e mun, hara himo e ﾉ殿nngannduyee immorde ka Joomi makko, wa'ata wa yoora ﾉ兎nrdeejo e jantagol Allah? ﾆ‘ fotataa fes. Tawde ko feewuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, daﾉ預ta, yoora ﾉ兎rﾉ容'en e jantagol Allah .ﾆ‘n wonii e majjere ﾉ殿nngunde."
  39,23,"Allah jppinii e Nulaaﾉ熔 Makko on Muhammadu (yo o his) Alqur'aana, ﾉ砥rnde moﾆｴﾆｴude yewtere. O waﾉ擁 nden nanndude ka goonga, e ka moﾆｴﾆｴugol, e ka yuﾉ橡登ndirgol e waasde luutondirde. Fillayeeji e ﾃｱaawooje hino ﾉ蓉uﾉ擁 e mayre, kaﾃｱum e fodooje e kammbaa, e sifaaji yimﾉ兎 goonga, e yimﾉ兎 meere ﾉ兎n ekn. Guri ﾉ兎n hulooﾉ兎 Joomi mun, hino riﾉ妬ra sabu nanugol kammbaaji ko woni e mayre, refti guri e ﾉ兎rﾉ容 maﾉ橡兎 deeﾆｴira jantagol Innde Allah, tuma ﾉ兎 nani jortagol e welo-welo ko woni e mayre. Koo ko jantaa e ko Alqur'aana battinta, ko peewal Allah, ngal O fewnirta mo O muuyani, O hoyna mo Mo O muuyani. Kala non mo Allah fewnaali, haray fewnoowo mo alaa."
  39,24,"Kere on mo Allah fewni aduna, O naadoya mo Aljanna laakara, on fotay wa yedduﾉ熔 maayi e keeferaaku on, naatoyoowo Yiite, tonnge juuﾉ容 e koyﾉ容, mo tawata waawoytaa daﾉ擁rde Yiite ngen, si wanaa tun o fewtinira nge yeeso makko ngon? Tooﾃｱuﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n feliree wi'aneede ontuma: meeﾉ容n non hannde, kon ko wonunoﾉ熔n faggitorde geddi e keeferaaku. Ko njoﾉ電i mon ndin nii."
  39,25,"Mofte adinooﾉ兎 ﾉ兎e sirkooﾉ兎, kadi fennuno Nulaaﾉ兎 mun, lepte ﾉ容n ardirani ﾉ兎 juhal, fewndo ka ﾉ兎 so'aa-anndude, sakko ﾉ兎 hebiloranaﾉ容 tuubugol."
  39,26,"Allah meeﾉ擁riﾉ兎 sabu ﾉ蓉m, lepte koyeera, e jaasere, e wirtere ka ngurrndam aduna. Pellet, ko lepte laakara ﾉ容n habbitiiﾉ容 ﾉ兎, ﾉ砥ri mawnude e tiiﾉ容, si tawno hiﾉ兎 anndunoo."
  39,27,"Gomﾉ擁i Men piyanii yimﾉ兎 ﾉ兎n, e ndee Alqur'aanaare jippinaande e Muhammadu (yo o his) noone kala e mise moﾆｴﾆｴere e bone, goonga e meere, gomﾉ擁nal e keeferaaku, ekn. ﾆ隔m fow, ko jortagol nde ﾉ兎 waajitora, ﾉ兎 huutora goonga kan, ﾉ兎 sela meere nden."
  39,28,"Men waﾉ擁 nde Alqur'aanaare, janngeteende e haala Aarabu, nde aldaa e ooﾃｱaare maa jiﾉ妬-liﾉ妬, jortagol no ﾉ兎 hulira Allah, jokkugol yamiraaﾉ擁 Makko, woﾉ遼擁too haﾉ預aﾉ擁 Makko."
  39,29,"Allah waﾉ擁i misal hakkunde sirkoowo e wootinﾉ擁noowo, woni gorko mo lurruﾉ兎 hawti : si o weltinii woﾉ遼兎 ﾉ兎n, ﾉ兎ya ﾉ兎n monoo, o wona e jiﾉ妬-liﾉ妬. Oya gorko, ko laaﾉ殿nﾉ熔 gorko goo, kanko tun, himo anndi ko deeﾆｴinta oya, e ko wallinta mo ﾉ兎rnde. ﾆ‘n worﾉ兎 ﾉ擁ﾉ熔, ﾉ兎 fotataa e misal. Yettoore woodanii Allah. Kono ko ﾉ砥ri ﾉ蓉uﾉ蓉de e maﾉ橡兎, ﾉ兎 anndaa. Ko waﾉ擁 si ﾉ兎 kafida e Allah, goﾉ遼蓉m goo."
  39,30,"Pelelt, an Nulaaﾉ熔, ko a maayoowo, kamﾉ兎 kadi ko ﾉ兎 maayooﾉ兎, feere mun alaa."
  39,31,"Refti onon ﾉ兎e yimﾉ兎, ﾃ疎lnde Darngal, ko ka Joomi mon yeddondiroyton, e ko pooﾉ熔ndiraynoﾉ熔n fii mun, goonguﾉ熔 on seerta e meerenteejo on."